PN,31404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1777327868
OL,3,CMPs to vote on whether PM should be
OL,4,Cinvestigated for misleading parliament
OL,6,FBut what is the Privileges Committee,
OL,7,Fand what is the case against the PM?
OL,8,FITV News explains.
OL,10,FWhat is the Privileges Committee?
OL,12,FThe Privileges Committee is a cross-
OL,13,Fparty committee of MPs who have the
OL,14,Fpower to investigate MPs alleged to
OL,15,Fhave breached parliament's rules and
OL,16,Fstandards.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1777327868
OL,3,CMPs to vote on whether PM should be
OL,4,Cinvestigated for misleading parliament
OL,6,FIt has the power to recommend
OL,7,Fsanctions if it finds rules have been
OL,8,Fbroken, though it would be up to the
OL,9,Fwhole of the Commons to vote on
OL,10,Fwhether these are implemented.
OL,12,FThe committee gained significant
OL,13,Fpublic attention when it investigated
OL,14,Fformer Prime Minister Boris Johnson
OL,15,Fover whether he misled parliament
OL,16,Fabout Partygate during the coronavirus
OL,17,Fpandemic.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1777327868
OL,3,CMPs to vote on whether PM should be
OL,4,Cinvestigated for misleading parliament
OL,6,FIn June 2023, the committee published
OL,7,Ftheir investigation into Johnson,
OL,8,Fwhich found that he had been
OL,9,Fmisleading when he told parliament
OL,10,Fthat Covid lockdown rules had been
OL,11,Ffollowed in Downing Street, when they
OL,12,Fhad not.
OL,14,FJohnson resigned as an MP before
OL,15,Fparliament could vote on it, accusing
OL,16,Fit of being a "kangaroo court".
OL,18,FWhy do some MPs think the prime
OL,19,Fminister misled parliament?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1777327868
OL,3,CMPs to vote on whether PM should be
OL,4,Cinvestigated for misleading parliament
OL,6,FQuestions over whether Starmer misled
OL,7,FMPs focus on previous statements he
OL,8,Fmade about appointing Mandelson as
OL,9,FWashington ambassador.
OL,11,FAfter Mandelson was first sacked, the
OL,12,Fprime minister repeatedly told MPs
OL,13,F"due process" was followed in the
OL,14,Fformer ambassador's appointment.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1777327868
OL,3,CMPs to vote on whether PM should be
OL,4,Cinvestigated for misleading parliament
OL,6,FSome MPs are questioning whether
OL,7,FMandelson's appointment really could
OL,8,Fbe called "due process" after it
OL,9,Femerged UK Security Vetting advised
OL,10,Fnot to grant him security clearance,
OL,11,Fbut were overruled by the Foreign
OL,12,FOffice.
OL,14,FOthers point to the advice given by
OL,15,Fthe then Cabinet Secretary Simon Case,
OL,16,Fwho told Starmer he should have his
OL,17,Fpick of political appointees vetted
OL,18,Fbefore confirming the appointment.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1777327868
OL,3,CMPs to vote on whether PM should be
OL,4,Cinvestigated for misleading parliament
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FThe second claim relates to the
OL,12,Fevidence given by the former Foreign
OL,13,FOffice chief Sir Olly Robbins, who was
OL,14,Falso sacked by Starmer over the
OL,15,Fvetting scandal.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31410
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1777327868
OL,3,CMPs to vote on whether PM should be
OL,4,Cinvestigated for misleading parliament
OL,6,FSpeaking during prime minister's
OL,7,Fquesitons, the PM told MPs the
OL,8,Fevidence given by Robbins to the
OL,9,FForeign Affairs Select Committee was
OL,10,Fthat "no pressure existed whatsoever"
OL,11,Fon the Foreign Office to appoint
OL,12,FMandelson.
OL,14,FThis appears to contradict what
OL,15,FRobbins told the committee when he
OL,16,Fsaid he experienced "constant
OL,17,Fpressure" and an "atmosphere of
OL,18,Fconstant chasing."
OL,20,FWhy is it complicated?
OL,26,@rD@FOUrD@eO]xD@UOUyD@IO]yD@ROUzD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31411
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1777327868
OL,3,CMPs to vote on whether PM should be
OL,4,Cinvestigated for misleading parliament
OL,6,FDocuments released by the government
OL,7,Fshow the prime minister did not know
OL,8,FMandelson had failed his security
OL,9,Fvetting when he told parliament due
OL,10,Fprocess had been followed.
OL,12,FMPs, including reports of at least one
OL,13,Fcabinet minister, have questioned why
OL,14,FRobbins had to lose his job in the
OL,15,FForeign Office if everything had been
OL,16,Fdone by the book.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31412
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1777327868
OL,3,CMPs to vote on whether PM should be
OL,4,Cinvestigated for misleading parliament
OL,6,FStarmer himself told MPs the evidence
OL,7,F"put to bed" allegations he had been
OL,8,Fdishonest, and an investigation by the
OL,9,Fprivileges committee will examine
OL,10,Fwhether he had done so inadvertently.
OL,12,FWhether the PM misled parliament in
OL,13,Fhis characterisation of Robbins'
OL,14,Fevidence to the select committee is
OL,15,Falso debated by some.
OL,17,FWhilst the PM said "no pressure
OL,18,Fexisted whatsoever", Robbins told MPs
OL,19,Fhe experienced "constant pressure" and
OL,20,Fan "atmosphere of constant chasing."
OL,26,@|D@DOU|D@dO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31413
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1777327868
OL,3,CMPs to vote on whether PM should be
OL,4,Cinvestigated for misleading parliament
OL,6,FThe former civil servant, however, did
OL,7,Falso say: "My life might have been
OL,8,Fconsiderably easier over the last two
OL,9,For three days if I wanted to come to
OL,10,Fthis committee and say I was put under
OL,11,Fsuch pressure, I just agreed to it.
OL,12,FBut that wouldn't be true."
OL,14,FHe also said: "Whilst I think the
OL,15,Fdepartment felt under pressure, we
OL,16,Fwere proud of the fact we'd not bow to
OL,17,Fthat pressure... In this case, I
OL,18,Fdidn't feel under that pressure
OL,19,Fpersonally in terms of my judgement."
OL,21,FShould the PM be worried?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31414
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1777327868
OL,3,CMPs to vote on whether PM should be
OL,4,Cinvestigated for misleading parliament
OL,6,FLabour's large majority makes it
OL,7,Fdifficult to lose votes in the
OL,8,FCommons, and the PM may choose to whip
OL,9,Fhis MPs to vote against an
OL,10,Finvestigation, something critics argue
OL,11,Fmay damage his own reputation.
OL,13,FIn 2022, Johnson allowed himself to be
OL,14,Freferred to the committee without
OL,15,Fcalling on his own MPs to oppose it.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31415
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1777327868
OL,3,CMPs to vote on whether PM should be
OL,4,Cinvestigated for misleading parliament
OL,6,FEven if Starmer wins the vote and
OL,7,Favoids an investigation, his standing
OL,8,Fcould be damaged by MPs within his own
OL,9,Fparty who choose to vote for it, or
OL,10,Feven rebel against the Labour whip,
OL,11,Frisking their own expulsion from the
OL,12,Fparty.
OL,14,FResponding to the speaker's decision
OL,15,Fto allow this issue to proceed to a
OL,16,Fvote, a Downing Street spokesperson
OL,17,Fsaid: "The government is engaging with
OL,18,Fthe two parliamentary processes that
OL,19,Fare already running on Peter
OL,20,FMandelson's appointment with full
OL,21,Ftransparency.
OL,26,@yD@GOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
