FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31416
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1777327868
OL,3,CMPs to vote on whether PM should be
OL,4,Cinvestigated for misleading parliament
OL,6,F"This is a desperate political stunt
OL,7,Fby the Conservative Party the week
OL,8,Fbefore the May elections because they
OL,9,Fhave no answers on the cost of living
OL,10,For the NHS. Their claims have no
OL,11,Fsubstance."
OL,13,FThe vote and debate will also add to
OL,14,Fthe prime minister's woes on Tuesday,
OL,15,Fwhich will see both former Foreign
OL,16,FOffice civil servant Phillip Barton,
OL,17,Fand the prime minister's former chief
OL,18,Fof staff Morgan McSweeney give
OL,19,Fevidence to the Foreign Affairs Select
OL,20,FCommittee.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/17
