CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1777327868
OL,3,CMPs to vote on whether PM should be
OL,4,Cinvestigated for misleading parliament
OL,6,FThe PM will then have to face
OL,7,Fquestions again on Wednesday for a
OL,8,Ffinal PMQs as parliament is expected
OL,9,Fto still be in session to complete the
OL,10,Ffinal stages of several government
OL,11,Fbills.
OL,13,FFrom Westminster to Washington DC -
OL,14,Four political experts are across all
OL,15,Fthe latest key talking points. Listen
OL,16,Fto the latest episode below...
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G17/17
